             was indicted for <rs id="t18050918-102-off545" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-off545" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-off545" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050918-102-cd546" type="crimeDate">17th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050918-102-off545 t18050918-102-cd546"></join>, forty yards of printed calico, value 36 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050918-102-victim933" type="victimName">
                     Abel 
                     Richards
                  <interp inst="t18050918-102-victim933" type="surname" value="Richards"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-victim933" type="given" value="Abel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-victim933" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050918-102-off545 t18050918-102-victim933"></join>
                  </persName>
               
            .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18050918-102-person934">
                  JAMES 
                  LANE
               <interp inst="t18050918-102-person934" type="surname" value="LANE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-person934" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-person934" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - On the 17th of August, a quarter before eight o'clock in the evening, I was going up Oxford-road, I saw the prisoner take the piece of calico from the form which stood at the door; I was some distance from him, I went after him immediately, and asked him what he was about; he answered me, what is that to you.</p>
               <p>Q. Were you near enough to be sure the prisoner was the man? - A. Yes, I caught hold of him by the collar, and he dropped the piece of calico on the pavement; I took it up, and took the prisoner and the calico into the shop; I produce the property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18050918-102-person935">
                  JOHN 
