                     <interp inst="t18050918-102-person935" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I live with Mr. 
               <persName id="t18050918-102-person936">
                  Abel 
                  Richards
               <interp inst="t18050918-102-person936" type="surname" value="Richards"></interp>
